dc_description_s: This data layer represents addresses for Sheboygan County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature dataset within the geodatabase NSheboygan_Addresses_2018.gdbN. [Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments. Sheboygan County Planning & Conservation Department assigns and enters all addresses outside of Cities & Villages. All City & Village addresses are entered when the Planning Department is informed of them.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
